  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Slice the focaccia bread in half lengthwise and place on a baking sheet.",
    "Drizzle the olive oil over the bread and sprinkle with minced garlic.",
    "Top the bread with chopped sardines, parsley, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Drizzle the lemon juice over the sardines.",
    "Cover the baking sheet with aluminum foil and steam for 10 minutes.",
    "Remove the foil and bake for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for a few minutes before serving."
